pan></strong>要製造的<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">焦點轉移</span></strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選</span>，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ef952d135304170ec0fac2d0d5a7929cd41206f4","tid":1728582,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"Push 勿戀陣地戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1</a><br />\n深度分析，大家可以都睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdbe96c3dc82a740606257c172fe0d160f810fd","tid":1728582,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}